      </article>
      <article class="faq-item">
        <h3>Can I get help with my account?</h3>
        <p>Yes! Our support team can help with account issues, billing questions, and technical problems.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="faq-item">
        <h3>Where can I report a bug?</h3>
        <p>You can report bugs through our contact form or by emailing us directly with details about the issue.</p>
      </article>
    </section>
  </section>
